The paper deals with domain adaptation in deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, since the paper focuses on image classification tasks, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The other sub-categories are also relevant as they involve machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques that are used in the proposed method.
